info.author: Tim Wegener
classifiers: Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.description:
Provide a dictionary-style object with reverse-lookup capabilities. This
integrity of the two-way mapping is maintained (must be a one-to-one) mapping.
Provides extra methods for reverse look-up such as key, get_key, has_value and
reversed_items.

This requires Python 2.2 or greater.
info.name: two_way_dict
